        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
            <head>Scope and Content </head>
            <p>Commission appoints Richard Royall, John Archer, John Archer, Jr., Richard Eppes,
                Seth Ward, Edward Osborne, Jr., Robert Kennon, Archibald Cary, John Markham, John
                Hylton, Abraham Saller, Peter Johnston, Christian Worsham, and Edward Friend
                justices for a court of Oyer and Terminer in Chesterfield County, Virginia to try
                Bob, the slave of Thomas Branch, for murder. </p>
        </scopecontent>
